+/*
+ * MFD core driver for Intel Cherrytrail Whiskey Cove PMIC
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2017 Hans de Goede <hdegoede@redhat.com>
+ *
+ * Based on various non upstream patches to support the CHT Whiskey Cove PMIC:
